data.description: POTENTIAL OPPORTUNITY TO ASSUME THE CURRENT INTEREST RATE AT 3.375%. Chelsea Schools*** 4 bedrooms*** Over 2,300 square feet ready for its new loving owners. The main level has a large beautiful dining room, half bath, open kitchen with large island, HUGE walk in pantry, large living area with lots of windows for natural lighting and a gas fire place to keep you cozy. Upstairs you will find a large loft area, four bedrooms, and laundry room. The master bedroom has a seating area, large walk in closet, and plenty of space. The master bath has double vanities, a garden tub, shower and private water closet.  The other three bedrooms are great sizes and share a spacious bathroom with a tub/shower combo.  Outside in the fenced in back yard there is plenty of room for entertaining and all the fun outdoor games.
